1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,170
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:01:57,130 --> 00:01:58,960
Gray Fullbuster...

5
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,870
You are far stronger than the 
information I gathered would imply...

6
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:04,970
Gray!

7
00:02:04,970 --> 00:02:06,780
I have to hurry and...

8
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:08,690
...find Erza!

9
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,080
Gray, hang in there!

10
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:15,110
Or perhaps his feelings for his friends 
strengthened his magical powers?

11
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:17,610
Natsu, wake up!

12
00:02:17,610 --> 00:02:19,500
The world is spinning...

13
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:24,940
You joined a splendid guild, Erza...

14
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,130
Destiny!

15
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,840
Charging towers are in place!

16
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,840
No anomalies!

17
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,260
Activating transference lacrima!

18
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,830
Preparing magic power compressors!

19
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:38,760
Beginning target status updates!

20
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,490
Space-time coordinates set!

21
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:41,210
Shall we charge the elements?

22
00:02:40,490 --> 00:02:41,960
Wait until merger is complete!

23
00:02:41,210 --> 00:02:42,720
Hurry calculating the compression!

24
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:45,720
Satellite Square, prepare for transfer!

25
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,720
Preliminary movement, check!

26
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:48,030
Beginning elemental merger!

27
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,960
Mountain's effect on wavelength, large!

28
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:50,580
Recalculating space-time coordinates!

29
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:56,760
It's no use... I can't move a finger...

30
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:59,230
I guess I used up too 
much of my magical power.

31
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:02,690
It doesn't look like Juvia can move either.

32
00:03:03,370 --> 00:03:04,990
What are we going to do?

33
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:08,250
We had our butts licked good...

34
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:10,230
Oh, someone's collapsed over there.

35
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:11,540
That voice!

36
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:13,370
I found you.

37
00:03:13,370 --> 00:03:16,100
Wait, we're not enemies anymore!

38
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:18,710
...is what I'd like to 
say, but I'm too scared!

39
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:21,600
Magical power 60% charged!

40
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:22,570
Etherion elements 47% merged!

41
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:24,560
27 minutes until arrival above target!

42
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:28,830
To think we'd be pressured 
into this course of action

43
00:03:28,830 --> 00:03:30,960
while the Council Chair is ailing...

44
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,280
It cannot be helped.

45
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:37,230
While the Chair is absent, it is us 9 who are 
responsible for the stability of the magical world.

46
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:40,440
Do not worry so much, Org.

47
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:43,530
Even if we are attacking another 
country with magic unprovoked,

48
00:03:43,530 --> 00:03:48,780
we can justify it under clause 27, paragraph 
4 of the National Security and Safety Act!

49
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:51,250
This isn't a matter of law.

50
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:54,160
We are about to fire Etherion.

51
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:56,260
We're doing evil!

52
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:59,180
It's Zeref who is the true evil here.

53
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:04,270
We can only pray that Etherion will 
be our saving grace and destroy Zaref!

54
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:08,650
It won't be long, Lord Sieg...

55
00:04:08,650 --> 00:04:09,500
Yes.

56
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,860
The dream you've had for 8 
years will become a reality.

57
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,980
Are you not afraid, Ultear?

58
00:04:14,980 --> 00:04:16,930
No, not even a little.

59
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:20,610
Because I always have complete 
faith in you, Lord Sieg.

60
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:24,740
I suppose so. There is 
no danger to your life.

61
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,010
True...

62
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,620
I am shaking a little...

63
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:31,620
If I fail, then I will be annihilated.

64
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:33,080
What?

65
00:04:33,470 --> 00:04:37,740
But this is very much worth 
risking one's life for.

66
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:42,090
Because this is my dream.

67
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,650
Yes.

68
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,430
Another 25 minutes, then?

69
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:52,430
I'll never see you again.

70
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:54,610
...Siegrain.

71
00:04:54,930 --> 00:04:58,150
Jellal!

72
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:01,420
Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!

73
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:03,490
How dare you trick us!

74
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:04,570
Sho!

75
00:05:04,570 --> 00:05:06,460
You hurt Sister!

76
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:08,110
Enough! Calm down!

77
00:05:08,470 --> 00:05:10,750
Let me out of here!

78
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:11,580
It's okay!

79
00:05:12,130 --> 00:05:13,860
I will protect you!

80
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:14,950
For sure!

81
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:15,960
Sho!

82
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,600
I am named Ikaruga.

83
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:45,360
Who are you?

84
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:48,280
Outta my way! Who is this crazy broad?

85
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:51,160
Oh, my! Aren't you unrefined?

86
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,290
I don't have any business with you!

87
00:05:58,710 --> 00:06:00,390
Imposs... ible!

88
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:04,460
There is nothing which I cannot cut.

89
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:07,050
What are you, some street performer?

90
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:11,590
What is this? My body...

91
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:18,440
I severed your nerves without 
cutting your clothes or flesh.

92
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:21,050
That is the essence of the New Moon School.

93
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:23,260
Sho!

94
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:24,520
Sister...

95
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:29,150
Oh, so that is where you were, Miss Erza...

96
00:06:29,150 --> 00:06:31,260
Let me out of here this instant!

97
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:33,140
She is not an opponent you can defeat!

98
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:36,850
Don't worry... That card is protected.

99
00:06:36,850 --> 00:06:39,760
There is no way anything from 
the outside could harm you.

100
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,860
Oh?

101
00:06:42,770 --> 00:06:44,930
That sounds like a challenge.

102
00:06:44,930 --> 00:06:46,500
Sho, get me out of here!

103
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:49,630
That is not a normal sword she has!

104
00:06:49,630 --> 00:06:52,200
Don't worry... Believe in me...

105
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:55,600
See?

106
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:00,810
She sliced through the spatial divide?

107
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,490
Sister...

108
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:18,200
Thanks to you, your sword made 
distortions in this space.

109
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:20,750
That's how I managed to cut my way out.

110
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,980
A sword that can cut through the 
spatial divide is amazing enough,

111
00:07:23,980 --> 00:07:26,750
but to use the enemy's slices 
in that split second...

112
00:07:27,110 --> 00:07:30,420
This is Titania's power...

113
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:32,610
You called yourself Ikaruga, yes?

114
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:34,510
I have no use for you.

115
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,510
Begone.

116
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:39,060
In lieu of an introduction...

117
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,310
No way!

118
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:48,750
Oh? Did you perhaps not see it?

119
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:56,500
That at which you gaze...

120
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:59,610
...beyond the mist, could it be...

121
00:07:59,610 --> 00:08:03,020
...a mononoke?

122
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,510
Trying so hard to find Jellal,

123
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:12,170
you no longer see the flash 
of swords all around you.

124
00:08:13,090 --> 00:08:15,600
Yes, yes... Those are the eyes...

125
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:18,120
She's getting serious now!

126
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:21,480
I am no mere passerby.

127
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,870
That is how it seems.

128
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:26,690
You are an enemy.

129
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:28,770
Come at me.

130
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:38,030
Heaven's Wheel, Circle Sword!

131
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,300
New Moon School.

132
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:46,920
Demon Flash.

133
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,460
All the swords were...

134
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,620
New Moon School.

135
00:08:58,420 --> 00:08:59,760
Sister!

136
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,140
Garuda Flame!

137
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:08,970
The Flame Empress Armor?

138
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:11,600
That armor has the ability to 
defend against flames, yes?

139
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:14,780
You do well to requip in such an instant.

140
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:21,610
You mustn't let his lordship 
see you looking like that, yes?

141
00:09:21,610 --> 00:09:25,500
What will you do? Will you don 
your strongest armor soon?

142
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,590
Damn monster...

143
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:32,320
You'd best repent!

144
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:35,010
Purgatory Armor, Requip!

145
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:39,220
There is no one that can stand 
when faced with this visage!

146
00:09:40,190 --> 00:09:42,510
So that's your strongest armor?

147
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:44,520
Come at me.

148
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:14,050
Do you not yet understand?

149
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:19,000
No matter what armor you don, 
you cannot win against my sword.

150
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,700
Give up, now.

151
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:24,920
S-She can't win...

152
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:28,300
She can't win!

153
00:10:34,330 --> 00:10:36,270
Wait, what's that armor?

154
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:38,090
Or wait, it's some outfit?

155
00:10:38,090 --> 00:10:40,200
What are you trying?

156
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:43,580
That outfit is nothing but cloth.

157
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:44,710
What?

158
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:47,330
Do you think so little of me?

159
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:50,440
Sister, what are you doing?

160
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:53,100
You've got to have a lot of 
strong armor left, right?

161
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:55,280
You're stronger than this, right?

162
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:57,320
I am...

163
00:10:58,130 --> 00:11:00,340
I am not strong.

164
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:02,940
Strength is...

165
00:11:04,490 --> 00:11:06,510
I like being by myself.

166
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:08,450
I feel uncomfortable around other people.

167
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:12,750
Then why are you crying all by yourself?

168
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:18,570
Before my eyes, countless numbers of 
my friends have become sacrifices.

169
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,880
I wasn't able to protect those dear to me.

170
00:11:22,410 --> 00:11:23,240
And then...

171
00:11:25,430 --> 00:11:27,070
I wasn't crying!

172
00:11:28,770 --> 00:11:31,250
I was always crying.

173
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:35,760
To be seen as strong...

174
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:39,150
...I shut my own crying heart...

175
00:11:40,330 --> 00:11:41,810
...inside of my armor.

176
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:47,600
I always wear armor because I am weak!

177
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:50,560
I could never take it off...

178
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:56,560
I will cut down my opponents, 
even if they are naked.

179
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:59,810
I believed that the armor would protect me.

180
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:01,740
But I was mistaken.

181
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:06,780
That armor blocked the space that separates 
people's hearts from one another.

182
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,200
Fairy Tail taught me this...

183
00:12:10,330 --> 00:12:14,540
It taught me how close people are to 
one another... How warm they are...

184
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,970
Sister...

185
00:12:19,330 --> 00:12:21,270
I am lost no longer!

186
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:25,210
I will turn my entirety to 
strength and have at you!

187
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:57,370
This battle is over.

188
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:05,130
Impressive...

189
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:10,530
Wow! You really are amazing, Sister!

190
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,810
Are you unharmed, Sho?

191
00:13:11,810 --> 00:13:13,350
Yes, somehow...

192
00:13:14,450 --> 00:13:20,060
This is the first time I've lost 
since I entered the guild...

193
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:24,450
But you and Jellal will all lose...

194
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,740
What's that supposed to mean?

195
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:28,610
15 minutes...

196
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:33,130
The light of justice...

197
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:36,260
...will rain down from the heavens...

198
00:13:36,260 --> 00:13:38,870
...and kill everyone.

199
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:44,560
That poem is dreadful...

200
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,250
Is she talking about Etherion?

201
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:49,990
Sho, take Simon and the others plus 
all the people from Fairy Tail,

202
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:51,710
and get away from this tower!

203
00:13:51,710 --> 00:13:53,220
B-But...

204
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:57,230
Will you do as I ask, Sho?

205
00:13:59,190 --> 00:14:00,230
Yeah...

206
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,390
What about you?

207
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:07,350
I will finish this.

208
00:14:12,780 --> 00:14:14,000
Huh?

209
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,880
Are you awake, Natsu?

210
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:19,290
I remember I was caught by some 
weird moving vehicle and...

211
00:14:19,290 --> 00:14:21,830
Stop! You can't get nausea from memories!

212
00:14:23,210 --> 00:14:25,530
After that you were eaten by Fukuro,

213
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:27,160
and Gray had to save you.

214
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:28,090
Gray?

215
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:31,960
But Gray took a lot of damage.

216
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,480
Erza...

217
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:35,200
You're heavy...

218
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,100
Gray, you got fat.

219
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,580
Shut it...

220
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:40,600
That cat is taking him out of here.

221
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:43,350
Satellite Square?

222
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:44,820
Don't joke about that!

223
00:14:43,610 --> 00:14:45,070
We have to evacuate!

224
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:47,780
But we'll be caught by the Fiore army!

225
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:50,170
That'd be better than 
getting hit by Etherion!

226
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:52,010
The ships are leaving...

227
00:14:52,010 --> 00:14:53,020
Look below you!

228
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:55,730
I found a ship!

229
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:57,540
That's the one we came in on.

230
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,390
I can't believe this!

231
00:15:00,390 --> 00:15:03,280
I lost, and Gray won?

232
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:05,510
You didn't really lose.

233
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:06,550
You were eaten.

234
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,880
He's gonna hold this over me for a month!

235
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:11,100
He's really petty like that...

236
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,410
Damn it!

237
00:15:12,410 --> 00:15:13,510
Come on now...

238
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:15,430
There's only one thing to do!

239
00:15:15,430 --> 00:15:19,180
Revenge! I'll fight that birdbrain 
again and get my revenge!

240
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:21,890
We don't have time for that!

241
00:15:21,890 --> 00:15:24,340
Oh yeah... Who are you?

242
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:25,670
Simon.

243
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:27,440
An old friend of Erza's.

244
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,910
Oh, okay. Nice to meetcha.

245
00:15:31,330 --> 00:15:32,640
You're injured?

246
00:15:33,190 --> 00:15:34,720
Don't worry about me.

247
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,690
Listen carefully, Natsu.

248
00:15:36,690 --> 00:15:38,970
Wally sent me a message before.

249
00:15:38,970 --> 00:15:43,460
He said he found Lucy and Juvia collapsed, 
along with a defeated member of Trinity Raven.

250
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,850
Lucy?

251
00:15:44,850 --> 00:15:47,600
They didn't know what was going on,

252
00:15:47,930 --> 00:15:50,660
so they took your two 
friends outside the tower.

253
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:53,440
Weren't these the enemy?

254
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,510
But Simon said they're our allies.

255
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:59,970
So then, why is she tying 
me up and dragging me?

256
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:05,940
And I've already been contacted by Sho 
that Trinity Raven have all been defeated.

257
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:07,690
I didn't do a thing!

258
00:16:07,690 --> 00:16:10,340
All that's left is Jellal himself.

259
00:16:10,340 --> 00:16:12,590
Erza is heading toward him now.

260
00:16:12,590 --> 00:16:13,700
Erza?

261
00:16:14,010 --> 00:16:17,960
She is trying to end this all by herself.

262
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:21,830
Those two have been connected 
by fate for 8 years.

263
00:16:22,210 --> 00:16:25,350
Their destiny may be to do battle.

264
00:16:26,130 --> 00:16:29,270
However Jellal is too powerful.

265
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:32,130
Please... Save Erza.

266
00:16:32,130 --> 00:16:33,590
Hell no.

267
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:34,880
What?

268
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:38,420
My, oh my...

269
00:16:38,420 --> 00:16:40,440
The game is already over?

270
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:43,600
Is playing with people's 
lives so fun for you?

271
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,260
It is fun.

272
00:16:45,260 --> 00:16:50,040
Birth and death, after all, are the 
origin and focus of all emotions.

273
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:54,320
Or to put it the other way around, 
nothing is more boring than living on its own.

274
00:16:55,410 --> 00:16:58,240
It has been a while, Erza...

275
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:01,070
Jellal...

276
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:06,760
I will liberate my past friends.

277
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,030
Do as you please.

278
00:17:08,030 --> 00:17:09,970
I no longer need them.

279
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:12,330
The Tower of Heaven has been completed.

280
00:17:12,330 --> 00:17:15,660
Even though it will be destroyed 
in less than 10 minutes?

281
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,700
You speak of Etherion?

282
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:21,760
Such confidence... So it was a bluff?

283
00:17:22,320 --> 00:17:23,520
No.

284
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:26,270
Etherion will rain down.

285
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:29,260
Hearing that makes me feel relieved.

286
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:34,740
If I can delay you by 10 minutes, 
then this will all be over!

287
00:17:34,740 --> 00:17:36,110
No.

288
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:39,730
You will be annihilated as Zeref's sacrifice.

289
00:17:39,730 --> 00:17:41,640
It has already been decided!

290
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:44,310
That is your fate.

291
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:45,750
Your destiny!

292
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:48,420
Damn it! Turn the ship around!

293
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:50,480
I can't do that, okay?

294
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:52,750
We were told to get away from here.

295
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:55,290
But Erza is still inside...

296
00:17:55,290 --> 00:17:56,480
And Natsu, too!

297
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:58,990
I'm sure she will be fine.

298
00:17:58,990 --> 00:18:00,220
I have to trust her.

299
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:03,690
I can't leave her to just Natsu!

300
00:18:03,690 --> 00:18:05,250
There's nothing to be done.

301
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:08,110
Simon is also with him... 
They'll handle it somehow.

302
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:10,820
Somehow? What's that supposed to mean?

303
00:18:10,820 --> 00:18:12,450
Don't yell!

304
00:18:12,450 --> 00:18:13,780
Everyone, calm down!

305
00:18:13,780 --> 00:18:16,680
Shut up! Turn the boat around now!

306
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,570
I've got to save Erza!

307
00:18:17,570 --> 00:18:19,000
Hurry, there's no time!

308
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,360
I said it's no use!

309
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:22,370
Shut up!

310
00:18:22,670 --> 00:18:25,670
What's with you? I want to go back, too!

311
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:27,510
But there's no point...

312
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:29,710
Etherion will fire any moment!

313
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:33,040
I just know that Natsu will bring Erza back!

314
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:35,610
That's what Simon told me!

315
00:18:35,610 --> 00:18:42,500
If Salamander's true power 
awakens, even Jellal wouldn't...

316
00:18:43,990 --> 00:18:45,140
Damn you!

317
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:48,290
Are you saying you aren't going 
to save Erza, your comrade?

318
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:51,440
Erza needs to defeat her own enemies.

319
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:53,870
It's not something I should butt in to.

320
00:18:54,290 --> 00:18:55,610
No.

321
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:58,780
Erza cannot win against Jellal.

322
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:00,310
Oh, yeah?

323
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:02,860
Don't put her down!

324
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:03,990
That's not it!

325
00:19:03,990 --> 00:19:06,670
I'm not talking about power or magic here...

326
00:19:06,670 --> 00:19:07,410
Yeah?

327
00:19:07,970 --> 00:19:12,470
Erza is still trying to save Jellal.

328
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,920
I know.

329
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:19,230
I know that she could 
never truly hate Jellal.

330
00:19:20,970 --> 00:19:23,250
Jellal is clever.

331
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:26,600
He will use those emotions of hers.

332
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:29,490
And that's not the worst of it.

333
00:19:29,490 --> 00:19:33,460
You know that the Council is trying to 
fire Etherion on this location, right?

334
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:37,270
If that happens, every human in 
this tower will be destroyed.

335
00:19:37,880 --> 00:19:41,650
According to Sho's message, 
we only have 10 more minutes.

336
00:19:41,650 --> 00:19:42,820
What?

337
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:46,950
She headed to face him alone after 
telling everyone to evacuate.

338
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:50,030
You know Erza well, yes?

339
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:56,880
I don't want to believe it, but she may be 
trying to use Etherion to take Jellal with her...

340
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,510
Why didn't you tell me that first?

341
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:04,090
Where is Erza?!

342
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:06,810
Seven more minutes.

343
00:20:06,810 --> 00:20:10,440
Seven more minutes and 
Etherion will rain down here.

344
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:13,440
Let's have fun for the 
next seven minutes, Erza.

345
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:15,850
Right now, I fear nothing.

346
00:20:16,170 --> 00:20:21,190
Even if Etherion comes, I will 
be satisfied to take you with me!

347
00:20:21,190 --> 00:20:23,280
Oh? Take me with you?

348
00:20:23,280 --> 00:20:25,400
Go ahead and try!

349
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:45,460
You finally finished the tower, and now 
you're destroying it? Don't you care, Jellal?

350
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:53,180
A pillar or two are nothing but decoration.

351
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:58,650
Sho and the others believed in you for 
eight years to make those decorations!

352
00:20:59,250 --> 00:21:02,480
Stop complaining about 
every little thing I say.

353
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:06,780
The important thing is the R-system. 
These eight years were for that.

354
00:21:07,610 --> 00:21:11,120
And that... is complete!

355
00:21:17,730 --> 00:21:22,300
It does seem you have improved a 
bit, but I guess that's your limit.

356
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:27,430
This isn't like you, Ms. Erza...

357
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:30,490
We'll lend you a hand.

358
00:21:30,490 --> 00:21:34,640
Even you get scared sometimes, right?

359
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:38,490
We're on your side, no matter what Erza!

360
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:41,410
Aye, we're the strongest team!

361
00:21:41,410 --> 00:21:45,920
I believed in you, Erza. I always 
did for these past 8 years.

362
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:47,490
Sister...

363
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,040
Everyone...

364
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:54,700
When we get back, fight me!

365
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:10,010
I thought I'd told you... 
Right now, I fear nothing!

366
00:22:11,650 --> 00:22:14,060
Is this really the same Erza?

367
00:23:56,180 --> 00:24:00,960
So this Satellite-something everyone's 
so worried about is what exactly?

368
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:05,320
Satellite Square! And why don't you know?

369
00:24:05,320 --> 00:24:09,980
It's an extremely powerful destructive spell 
that can destroy an entire city easily.

370
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:13,260
Wait, we're in deep trouble 
if we get hit by that!

371
00:24:13,260 --> 00:24:16,340
Next time: A Prayer Under the Holy Light.

372
00:24:16,340 --> 00:24:20,230
This won't do! Where is Erza?

373
00:24:20,230 --> 00:24:24,000
I pray that Natsu gets some common sense.

374
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,250


